      <merge>
        <title>The chat input field</title>
        <abstract>
          <para>
            The chat input field is located at the bottom of the &openwebui;
            chat window. Its main purpose is to accept a user prompt so that the
            AI can process it and respond (see
            <xref linkend="openwebui-chat-window-usage"/>). Besides that, the
            chat input field provides extended functionality that can help you
            achieve the following tasks.
