    <module renderas="section" xml:id="openwebui-setting-default-prompt">
      <merge>
        <title>Setting the default system prompt</title>
        <abstract>
          <para>
            In &openwebui;, you can set a system prompts in several
            contexts&mdash;for the current chat, for the current user, or for a
            specific AI model. While the prompt set for the current chat
            overrides the user and model prompts, the user-specific prompt
            overrides the model prompt only.
          </para>
        </abstract>
      </merge>
